        {
            "+content": "Takasaki Tomoka believed in her 15 years of life, she had finally found her prince.She never had managed to speak to him but she makes sure she takes a specific car of the train coming home from school knowing he would be there and she could stare at him from a distance.One such thursday, she bumps into a strange kansai accented boy,Miwazawa Arata on her way to school.Things start to change as this boy later offers her membership to his band-spiral.And the prince is in it too... except that its not a he but a she, Serika Yuuki.So she should give up on him/her.... but she can't forget her first love thus she joins the band and thus begins her dangerous love.Things are not easy for her especially since Arata falls for her and Serika tries to run away from her.Along with the cheerful incurable casanova Ogura Takemi and the silent and unencouraging Hakagama Tametsu and the others, Tomoka has a break into the music world as well.",
